title: Spittin' Chiclets Episode 141: Featuring Kevin Hayes
description:
On Monday's episode of Spittin' Chiclets the guys are joined by Kevin Hayes of the New York Rangers to check in on how his season is going. Haysie and the boys tell some stories and catch up on some things since the last time he joined the podcast, including some great stories about the infamous Keith Yandle. The guys also touch on some NHL news and how Rear Admiral is having the best week of his life.


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/schiclets
